name: Pretend Extinct
description:
Pretend Extinct

Agents from Area-51 have discovered that aliens are coming to destroy earth, our only hope is to pretend extinct! 

As an agent, use different tools to evacuate people and make the buildings look like abandoned. 

Can you trick the aliens and save earth? Credits

Augusto Correia Rocha
